Bluhdorn 11 – (7/12, Ingolfur, PhD, Reader in Politics/Political Sociology, University of Bath, “Ingolfur Blühdorn: The Sustainability Of Democracy,” http://www.thenewsignificance.com/2011/07/12/ingolfur-bluhdorn-the-sustainability-of-democracy/)
